Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.66,0:02:50.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定是一種
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.06,0:02:54.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,讓人心情舒暢的事情吧
