Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.02,0:03:05.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,想要把迷戀你的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:07.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,全部變成我的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.78,0:03:09.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.80,0:03:14.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算會傷害到別人也在所不惜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.74,0:03:17.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.38,0:03:24.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我很清楚我現在只考慮著自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:27.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但不知為何就是停不下來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.44,0:03:30.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要別人對她的好感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.48,0:03:33.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,想要贏過她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.66,0:03:40.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,否則 我會越來越空虛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.56,0:03:46.38,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,感情不是你爭我奪的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:48.16,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.28,0:03:52.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且絕對不可能靠搶奪而得到滿足
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.75,0:03:54.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了 給我閉嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.84,0:03:59.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可憐的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.10,0:04:02.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,幼稚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:07.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,自命清高的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:16.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:19.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還是交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.92,0:04:20.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:25.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們性情相合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.14,0:04:27.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一定能夠順利的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:34.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麥肯定也會喜歡上我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.86,0:04:38.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 不一起回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.36,0:04:40.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 有點事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.14,0:04:48.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,花火
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.86,0:04:51.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.36,0:04:56.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道自己膚淺又自私
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.06,0:05:01.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小繪 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.88,0:05:04.66,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,決定要和麥好好交往了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.56,0:05:07.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但無論如何只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:12.38,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只有小繪你我無法再繼續利用下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.76,0:05:17.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你是我重要的 唯一的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.29,0:05:19.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.09,0:05:22.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那又怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.96,0:05:26.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,利用我也行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.14,0:05:28.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:30.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,別擺出這副表情嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.42,0:05:32.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.80,0:05:35.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你心裡有數吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.26,0:05:37.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,現在總算體會到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:41.13,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是我的覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.36,0:05:50.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,從今以後…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.64,0:05:53.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會再在放學後單獨見你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.16,0:05:58.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:09.16,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對 我做了一件再也無法挽回的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.88,0:06:11.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我害怕得不敢回頭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.24,0:06:14.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不敢看你的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:17.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我必須去面對你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:19.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,原本該這麼做的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.18,0:06:22.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我至少要去做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.56,0:06:23.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.76,0:06:26.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.96,0:06:32.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,別想走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.90,0:06:34.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.96,0:06:36.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,放手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:47.24,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得頭好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.84,0:06:49.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天沒什麼睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.86,0:06:53.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,安樂岡同學也要去圖書館嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.48,0:06:58.38,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想去看書
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.42,0:06:59.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,教室太吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:00.40,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.60,0:07:04.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 畢竟老師不在嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:14.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,繪鳩同學也來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.01,0:07:17.54,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 可以一起坐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.91,0:07:18.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,請坐請坐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.61,0:07:22.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:27.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.50,0:07:31.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她在試圖用普通的方式對待我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.40,0:07:37.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,幹 幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.27,0:07:39.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在「學校」的話就沒問題了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.16,0:07:42.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,圖書館禁止交頭接耳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.16,0:07:43.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.66,0:07:50.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnSentyTEA 新蒂下午茶体\bord0\c&H959595&\fs105\frz351\frx16\fry356\pos(486,558)}被提醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.53,0:07:55.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs210\fnSentyTEA 新蒂下午茶体\bord0\c&H383839&\frz340.9\b0\frx12\fry354\pos(897,828)}安靜點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.68,0:08:02.55,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你原諒我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:05.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我依賴了你 利用了你 並踐踏了你的心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.94,0:08:09.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最終還將自己任性的願望強加於你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:14.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這是 我應得的報應
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.67,0:08:24.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,發燒的話早點跟我說不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.64,0:08:27.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒給我說的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:30.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.88,0:08:36.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:39.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不能這麼做 不停下來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.10,0:08:42.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用擔心任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.76,0:08:46.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有人知道我們的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.34,0:08:48.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 花火
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.76,0:08:50.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼又想和粟屋交往了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.50,0:08:53.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,想引起你喜歡的人的注意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:57.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我有喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:09:00.40,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.58,0:09:03.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明花火這樣就很有魅力了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.62,0:09:06.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,能讓花火不惜做到這地步也想要得到的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.55,0:09:07.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真讓人嫉妒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.26,0:09:09.71,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.92,0:09:12.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.32,0:09:16.88,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這種脆弱的一面就是花火的魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:21.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要攻略男人什麼的很簡單哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.24,0:09:25.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 不由得越來越想注視著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.80,0:09:27.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,被黑暗浸染著的你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.20,0:09:32.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今後 不管你遭到再多的玷汙與傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.89,0:09:36.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我都會接受你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.74,0:09:40.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 你要裝作敞開心扉的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.40,0:09:43.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,而不需要表現出
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.04,0:09:45.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.88,0:09:49.19,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,反而要永遠藏起來 不然內心就會壞掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:54.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我想要讓對方知道我的心意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:10:00.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,自己的事情到死之前只有自己知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.44,0:10:01.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這也沒什麼不好的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.42,0:10:04.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.66,0:10:09.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不知為何我覺得她或許也會說同樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.58,0:10:13.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以她的意思是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.10,0:10:17.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小繪的話聽起來隱約有種孤獨感
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.75,0:10:20.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這句話不就意味著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.42,0:10:24.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,任何人都是孤獨的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.74,0:10:26.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,連那傢伙也不例外
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.70,0:10:32.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,花火
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:34.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,花火 起來了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.79,0:10:37.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,去幫我買點東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.60,0:10:44.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,還有什麼沒買的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.58,0:10:48.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.60,0:10:53.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是茜的學生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.86,0:10:58.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在家庭餐廳見過的那人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.48,0:11:01.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 你忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.73,0:11:02.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真狂妄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.80,0:11:06.37,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,別碰我別靠近我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.35,0:11:09.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.49,0:11:10.81,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙也是茜的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.96,0:11:13.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你要裝作敞開心扉的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.20,0:11:17.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我當然記得你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.36,0:11:20.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,原來我們住的這麼近呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.72,0:11:23.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要攻略男人什麼的很簡單哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.20,0:11:37.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小花火…那什麼 告訴我你的聯絡方式嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.01,0:11:40.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊但你在家庭餐廳裡是和男朋友一起來著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.16,0:11:43.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭 不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.08,0:11:44.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.20,0:11:48.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣我們下次出去玩 好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.36,0:11:50.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.50,0:11:53.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣真的能填滿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.69,0:12:02.66,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是制服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.14,0:12:04.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為從學校回來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.80,0:12:07.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為JK是賣點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:19.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小花火還真是可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.62,0:12:20.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,經常被這樣說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.69,0:12:22.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這氣氛真糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:24.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可能會要接吻了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.77,0:12:28.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,完全沒有人這樣子說了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.96,0:12:30.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.64,0:12:32.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對…對了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.70,0:12:36.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個雖然有點在意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.74,0:12:40.38,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你和皆川老師是什麼關係啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.06,0:12:42.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 茜？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.59,0:12:47.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙啊 都腳踏幾條船了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.14,0:12:49.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能成為我的所有物的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.28,0:12:53.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以小花火和我交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.75,0:12:55.40,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.22,0:13:01.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對茜來說 這傢伙只是眾多男寵中的一員
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.36,0:13:04.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,即使如此這傢伙也想和她牽扯在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.23,0:13:10.66,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,反過來這傢伙 也想讓把我納入他的「眾人」之中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.89,0:13:13.16,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:16.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,慘不忍睹全無起色
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.46,0:13:20.66,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我 明明想勝過那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.22,0:13:22.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 吶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:25.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.10,0:13:28.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是處女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,0:13:32.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此 也能喜歡上我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:38.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,倒不如說 我不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.22,0:13:43.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 只有這種眼神才不會讓我討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.12,0:13:47.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我很渴望 能毫無弱點地面對著他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.59,0:13:50.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,澆灌著此時此地的我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.90,0:13:51.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:13:57.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,與喜歡的人接吻是怎樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:14:03.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那可能是與對這個世界一無所知是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.28,0:14:05.66,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為 因為一直以來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.35,0:14:07.62,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,每當我們相依相偎時
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.37,0:14:13.38,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我才感覺到我是如此的空虛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.32,0:14:16.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真實的情感被鑰匙上了鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.06,0:14:19.23,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,藏在了最深的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.03,0:14:23.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不被人 不被任何人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:27.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,賓館 去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.06,0:14:30.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.67,0:14:33.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊咧 不對嗎 我還以為你想去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.55,0:14:35.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我會很溫柔地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.51,0:14:38.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.40,0:14:39.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.87,0:14:45.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊不 心情問題…之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.16,0:14:50.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,身體舒服的話 心情也會輕易地跟上的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.29,0:14:53.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.04,0:14:58.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,用想著哥哥的心情與麥在一起時
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:15:00.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺非常的舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.80,0:15:08.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 就算這樣中間也一定有著對麥本身的渴求的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.30,0:15:11.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是軟弱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.60,0:15:14.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺你在考慮複雜的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.61,0:15:16.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.56,0:15:18.55,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,請別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.40,0:15:21.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.80,0:15:26.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,做舒服的事 感覺會變成笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.21,0:15:28.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:30.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.52,0:15:34.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得這是像你這種輕浮的人不會懂的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.92,0:15:36.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗚哇好過分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:37.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,回去算了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.55,0:15:40.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 差點就感情用事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.58,0:15:43.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可以感情用事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.26,0:15:45.78,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在擺什麼架子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.94,0:15:49.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對不是處女的自己沒自信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.49,0:15:53.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣你的價值也就這麼點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.33,0:15:58.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 怎麼了怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.80,0:16:04.39,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是因為很…害…怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.34,0:16:07.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.42,0:16:09.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉 慢慢來就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.38,0:16:13.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好險 差點就被煽動了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.92,0:16:18.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,從現在起開始習慣吧 一點點地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.75,0:16:20.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.28,0:16:23.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,演技我多少也能出賣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.34,0:16:27.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如此我能沉迷於虛幻的自己便可
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.04,0:16:31.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再聯絡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.11,0:16:35.71,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.30,0:16:38.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.62,0:16:42.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙與我不同
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.80,0:16:45.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最開始就把自己的價值放在高處
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.96,0:16:47.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,自尊心被填滿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.18,0:16:49.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也不會被消減
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.70,0:16:51.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,與此相比的我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.57,0:16:53.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(370,0)\fn@方正准圆_GBK\fs50\frz270\c&H000000&\b1\bord0\pos(1330.333,190.667)}真是可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.57,0:16:53.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(370,0)\fn@方正准圆_GBK\frz270\c&H000000&\b1\bord0\pos(1632,384)}好萌~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.57,0:16:53.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(370,0)\fn@方正准圆_GBK\frz270\c&H000000&\b1\bord0\pos(1587,738)}色色的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:53.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如他人的評價一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.26,0:16:56.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,藉此取回自己的自尊心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.28,0:16:58.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,此間相差甚遠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.22,0:17:03.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,把自己的存在價值寄託在他人身上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.34,0:17:07.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但那就像笨蛋一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.80,0:17:10.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像只要被那個人所否定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.47,0:17:11.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,世界就完了一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.17,0:17:15.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那感情是來自於
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.52,0:17:16.62,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.40,0:17:23.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說爸爸在小花出生後不久就不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.50,0:17:25.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,誰說的 那種話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.36,0:17:27.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,親戚們說的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.71,0:17:32.62,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸在哪裡組成了個新家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.12,0:17:36.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要小花了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.72,0:17:45.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小花什麼事也沒做錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.78,0:17:48.37,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,無論是多喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.64,0:17:50.84,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也會漸漸地疏遠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.22,0:17:53.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可能就不能在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.64,0:17:55.19,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎麼喜歡也？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.04,0:17:57.40,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小花和哥也？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:18:00.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小花和哥哥絕對不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.55,0:18:02.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.74,0:18:04.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 因為
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.82,0:18:07.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不可能相戀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.60,0:18:21.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,與喜歡的人接吻 我不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:28.75,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(2500,0)\bord0\fs105\fn@方正卡通_GBK\b0\frz267.3\pos(867,528)}暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.64,0:18:29.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好了休業式要開始了 移動到體育館去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.01,0:18:30.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.26,0:18:43.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.34,0:18:45.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,花火很受歡迎啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.26,0:18:48.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可不能掉以輕心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.14,0:18:51.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,掉以輕心？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.66,0:18:55.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,做過吧 花火也
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.44,0:18:57.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,做過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.66,0:19:03.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊不 都特地說了交往吧這樣的話了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.52,0:19:06.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不知道是誰 但再不退場就很奇怪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:10.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我又被腳踏兩條船了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.66,0:19:15.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,應該都差不多快消失了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.56,0:19:17.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來不得不再弄一個上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.00,0:19:28.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,去我家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.50,0:19:32.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不了 明天要早起還是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.84,0:19:36.81,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,接吻和平常一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.54,0:19:39.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是很擅長隱藏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.28,0:19:41.88,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.44,0:19:44.16,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,說白了會隱隱作痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.78,0:19:46.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我的渣女雷達
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.52,0:19:49.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.28,0:19:53.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不見了 最可
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.60,0:19:58.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那種女人 絕對不是真心對麥的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.24,0:20:02.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你一直以來都是這樣直接地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.64,0:20:04.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,讓人掃興
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.06,0:20:07.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.42,0:20:11.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麥要是喜歡她到就算這樣也行的地步的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.60,0:20:14.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.16,0:20:17.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 並不是這樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.86,0:20:19.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那為什麼我就不行了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.98,0:20:22.78,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也行的啊 你也
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.58,0:20:24.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明天要約會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:29.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊真是的 別哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.82,0:20:33.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是你理想的王子殿下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.30,0:20:37.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣說的話 會哭得更厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.78,0:20:40.23,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,確實有點可憐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.21,0:20:44.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺有點寵著最可呢我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.48,0:20:45.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,約會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.90,0:20:51.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麥像這樣邀請我可是第一次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:57.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我的喜歡是 即便如此也行的程度的喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.15,0:21:05.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\fs37.5\frx10\fry346\frz351.5\pos(777,591)}今天有空？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.15,0:21:05.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\fs37.5\frz350.7\frx354\fry350\pos(804,738)}沒空啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.15,0:21:05.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\fs37.5\frx10\fry346\frz347.4\pos(603,873)}擠點時間嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.15,0:21:05.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\fs37.5\frx10\fry346\frz348.2\pos(399,1065)}我想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.24,0:21:08.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,鑽進被窩 閉上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.88,0:21:10.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,數一下綿羊的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.72,0:21:18.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,醒來的時候你看 暑假就開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.24,0:02:40.24,Kuzu_text,,0,0,0,,
